data.description: 588 Trego Creek Road is situated on 1.23 beautiful acres. If you long for peaceful living in the country, but don't want to be too far from town, this property is perfect for you! The home has three bedrooms, two baths and has been very well maintained. The master bedroom features a gorgeous custom wood accent wall, a spacious closet and a master bath with a garden tub. The second bedroom also features a custom-built wood accent wall. The property includes a 10x16 storage shed with electricity and two lofts and an additional 7x7 storage shed. This home is a must-see!
